                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <strong>Focus Groups</strong>
                  <p class="text-sm">Facilitated discussions to explore issues in depth</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17v1a1 1 0 001 1h4a1 1 0 001-1v-1m3-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v7m3-2h6" />
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <strong>Data Analysis</strong>
                  <p class="text-sm">Review of absence, turnover, and performance data</p>
